INSTALLATION
============

Download the source code from the git repository:
	git clone http://trac.laas.fr/git/robots/morse.git

Create the directory 'build':
	mkdir build

Change to the new directory:
	cd build

Configure CMake:
	ccmake ..

Set the installation prefix directory. For example:
CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX      $HOME/openrobots

Make and install
	make; make install



Set the environment variable PYTHONPATH. It must include the installation directory of the morse scripts, and the path to the blender specific scripts.
For example:

tcsh
setenv PYTHONPATH $HOME/openrobots/lib/python2.6/site-packages:$HOME/openrobots/lib/python2.6/site-packages/morse/blender

bash
export PYTHONPATH=$HOME/openrobots/lib/python2.6/site-packages:$HOME/openrobots/lib/python2.6/site-packages/morse/blender


